---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="UK AI Search Visibility Research & Data | Rank4AI" description="Original research from 1,400+ UK business website audits. AI visibility statistics, case studies, weekly intelligence and methodology from Rank4AI.">

<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-tag">Research</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Research</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-[700px]">Original UK data from 1,400+ business website audits. No other AI search agency has this.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href="/research/uk-ai-visibility-stats/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">UK AI Visibility Statistics</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">26 original research data points from our audits. What we found when we tested 1,400+ UK business websites.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/research/case-studies/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Case Studies</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Real results for real businesses. How AI search visibility was measured, built, and improved.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/research/weekly-intelligence/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Weekly Intelligence</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">What changed in AI search this week. Platform updates, signal shifts, and what it means for UK businesses.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/research/methodology/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Methodology</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">How we test and measure AI search visibility. The 17-section audit methodology behind the Five Signal Model.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/research/rankings/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Rankings</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Industry rankings, agency comparisons, and landscape reports for the UK AI search market.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="teal-section py-20 px-10 mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
      <div><div class="font-display text-4xl text-accent-bright leading-none mb-2">1,400+</div><div class="text-sm text-text-light-muted">businesses audited</div></div>
      <div><div class="font-display text-4xl text-accent-bright leading-none mb-2">26</div><div class="text-sm text-text-light-muted">research data points</div></div>
      <div><div class="font-display text-4xl text-accent-bright leading-none mb-2">6</div><div class="text-sm text-text-light-muted">AI platforms tested</div></div>
      <div><div class="font-display text-4xl text-accent-bright leading-none mb-2">5</div><div class="text-sm text-text-light-muted">signal layers measured</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center py-24 px-10">
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
